    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Biomes characterized by hot, dry summers, and cool, moist winters and vegetation comprising aromatic herbs (sage, rosemary, thyme, oregano), shrubs, acacia, chamise, and grasses.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
